title: Hobby Horses Zelda (White, Medium) Hobby Horse, Includes Backpack, Passport, Ages 3+
features: Realistic Hobby Horse created for this popular sport. It allows you to simulate horseback riding, obstacle jumping and riding
The backpack and passport, which make it unique and customizable, are included in the purchase.
Head is made of plush, PP cotton filling. The stick made of pine wood. With a weight of 730 g in size L. With a weight of 630 g in size M.
Available in two sizes: Medium and Large size. Further dimensions can be found in the description in the photo gallery. Size L: length 74 cm, width 21 cm, size M: length 66 cm, width 14 cm
CE marking: All parts of the kit comply with the applicable requirements that the European Community imposes on toys, therefore safe for children aged 3 and up.
description: Product description Hobby Horses It is the perfect stable companion for any child who wants to spend hours riding in the gym, garden or at home. Complete with realistic head, braiding mane and wooden stick, the mini knights will have hours of fun running around with their mini horse.
